{"id": 2298, "genre": 1000, "title": "你是哪种化妆人格？", "description": "脸上涂鸦型如我。还有其他化妆体质欢迎在留言区自我揭露。（提图来自：istock ©NilouferWadia ）", "record_count": 8623, "comment_count": 33, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180423212001RsVz7CqJBuDcv4QF.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-04-23T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 4069, "title": "你是哪种化妆人格？", "content": "你是哪种化妆人格？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 277439, "content": "什么都不搞型，只护肤不化妆", "image": "img/option/option/20180423161047PU8G0ovyDd2tnYOb.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 277443, "content": "有心无力型，跟帖钻研数载依旧是门外汉", "image": "img/option/option/201804231614138hnqP2xuKF0adyIJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 277436, "content": "只涂口红型，显得气色好点就行", "image": "img/option/option/20180423160751e2ZIQTtBP10UozrL.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 277437, "content": "只化眉毛型（无眉星人的痛", "image": "img/option/option/20180423160901wb634v1kQzIFKCxO.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 277438, "content": "基本功型，有底妆就行", "image": "img/option/option/20180423160952OLwN4QFj3KuxC0Zz.gif", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 277440, "content": "重点眼妆型，眼睛才是美的第一窗口", "image": "img/option/option/20180423161157s62VeahgcPCWu5xI.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 277453, "content": "光影魔术手型，修容鼻影高光创造奇迹", "image": "img/option/option/20180423163820rGzW2VQkSOTdMcj1.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 277442, "content": "全套到位型，从隔离遮瑕到定妆不少于十步", "image": "img/option/option/201804231612462bP469wtQlUfYA81.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 277571, "content": "人间导师型，室友同事多少都向我取过经", "image": "img/option/option/20180423212850RsvGQtFxXbmuErV7.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}